# {{†}} [[form]]; [[shape]]; thing that has [[take shape|taken shape]]
#* {{zh-x|刑 者 侀{xíng} 也，侀{xíng} 者 成 也，一 成 而 不可 變，故 君子 盡心 焉。|Punishment may be compared to the body. The body is a complete thing; when once completed, there cannot be any subsequent change in it. Hence the wise man will do his utmost (in deciding on all these inflictions).|ref=Liji-L}}
